entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: You have gathered the raw chemical Coagulant and returned to Dak!
entries.journal_entry_description: Search the area around Mt. Chaolt for rocks containing deposits of raw Cationic Chemical Coagulant and take them to Dak Vox when you have gathered the amount he wants.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Chemical deposits can be mined around the area. Collect the deposits and return to the smuggler.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Return to Dak Vox with the raw Cationic Chemical Coagulant.
